headline: Cebu City, Philippines: Cloudflare's 138th Data Center
keywords: March of Cloudflare, Data Center, Cloudflare Network
description: Cebu City, the second most populous metro area, but oldest city in the Philippines is the home of Cloudflare’s newest Data Center.  Located centrally in the Philippines, Cebu has had a long standing tradition of trade and business activity, the word itself “Cebu” meaning trade.
